title: Subscribing To The Transcendent’s Channel
description: Subscribing To The Transcendent’s Channel Manhwa Living by selling information about monsters, Maeng Siwoo is considered completely useless in the hunter industry without any standout qualities. However, he fiercely battles to provide for his sick younger sibling. One fateful day, he is gifted a mysterious smartphone by a transcendent being within a dungeon, appointing him as the channel manager for such beings. Upon subscribing to the channel, he unlocks the ability to wield the powers of the gods. 초월자의 채널을 구독했다 Subscribed To The Transcendental Channels
